9 Sec. 17. (1) Prior to entering a new manufacturer-dealer agreement
10 to sell the same line-make, a dealer shall provide written notice to each
11 manufacturer and distributor with which the dealer has a manufacturer-
12 dealer agreement.
13 (2) Such written notice shall:
14 (a) Be provided to the headquarters of the manufacturer or
15 distributor at least thirty days prior to entering the new manufacturer-
