1 (d) If the prospective transferee is a family member of the dealer,
2 such family member intends to do any of the following without the consent
3 of the manufacturer or distributor:
4 (i) Relocate the dealership to any location; or
5 (ii) Alter the terms or conditions of the manufacturer-dealer
