27 replaced, if the warrantor requests for such part to be shipped to the
28 warrantor.
29 Sec. 24. A warrantor may ship parts to the dealer so that such
30 dealer will be able to carry out factory campaign work. If such parts are
31 in excess of a dealer's requirements, the dealer may return the unused
